"'''Waiting on You'''" is a song recorded by Canadian [[country music]] artist [[Charlie Major]]. It was released in 1996 as the fourth single from his second studio album, ''[[Lucky Man (Charlie Major album)|Lucky Man]]''. It peaked at number 2 on the ''[[RPM (magazine)|RPM]]'' Country Tracks chart in October 1996.

